commands: jq --arg buildroot "$FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR" --argjson data '{"git+https://git@github.com/Ian2020/npm-installer.git": "flatpak-node/git-packages/nw-8e1575a4abf16901924a6146835334ddeaa17b14#8e1575a4abf16901924a6146835334ddeaa17b14", "https://git@github.com/Ian2020/npm-installer.git": "flatpak-node/git-packages/nw-8e1575a4abf16901924a6146835334ddeaa17b14#8e1575a4abf16901924a6146835334ddeaa17b14"}' 'walk(    if type == "object"    then        to_entries | map(            if (.value | type == "string") and $data[.value]            then .value = "git+file:\($buildroot)/\($data[.value])"            else .            end        ) | from_entries    else .    end)' $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/onlykey-app/package.json > $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/onlykey-app/package.json.new

jq --arg buildroot "$FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR" --argjson data '{"git+https://git@github.com/Ian2020/npm-installer.git#8e1575a4abf16901924a6146835334ddeaa17b14": "flatpak-node/git-packages/nw-8e1575a4abf16901924a6146835334ddeaa17b14#8e1575a4abf16901924a6146835334ddeaa17b14", "https://git@github.com/Ian2020/npm-installer.git#8e1575a4abf16901924a6146835334ddeaa17b14": "flatpak-node/git-packages/nw-8e1575a4abf16901924a6146835334ddeaa17b14#8e1575a4abf16901924a6146835334ddeaa17b14"}' 'walk(    if type == "object" and (.version | type == "string") and $data[.version]    then        .version = "git+file:\($buildroot)/\($data[.version])"    else .    end)' $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/onlykey-app/package-lock.json > $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/onlykey-app/package-lock.json.new
